{"tid":367642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷：你以為一紙基本法就可以保証司法獨立？","createTime":"2017-08-21T01:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T05:37:35.000Z","uid":189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6f9ffe536e529120f85579c244bb016bd91cdd","tid":367642,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"有些人以為香港是一個民主社會，故香港的法律原則可以完全用民主國家的標準來討論，如怎樣看暴力的定義。有時候真的覺得這類人是無可救藥的天真。不是純真的那種，是無知的那種。我們明明是活在一個共產專制政權之下，你以為一紙基本法就可以保証司法獨立？你真的以為共產黨是披了狼皮的羊嗎？反過來，經過了那麼多年，騙了又騙，你竟還看不見共產黨是披了羊皮的狼？若不說你無知，我就真的無話可說了。"},{"pid":"d972c35ebd39d54e9c90d3f2d5a9232c61af3eba","tid":367642,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/757553237771773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F757553237771773&d=PUNy4RQsqhLpO4ases%2FIbI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fdb67863\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/757553237771773</a>"},{"pid":"8701232ccfe9e9dca0f05c8ae043747eabb2ad82","tid":367642,"uid":49279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"咁你又支持民主回歸?"},{"pid":"67bc62ff999b376b2db15d1b71546a508168c6ee","tid":367642,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:31:05.000Z","msg":"永續基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c07d6e8cc0bf2f4f27fa2e55b6b3d8f0f927b8d","tid":367642,"uid":28155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"我諗唔到有咩野可以天真得過民主回歸中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46313b65b55d7b048964a7185fde183d74034143","tid":367642,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗唔到有咩野可以天真得過民主回歸中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢當年以為共產黨係披了狼皮的羊，後來終於覺醒，應該比個機會佢悔改啦，好過好多廢中廢老今時今日仲當共產黨係太陽"}]}